Sturmik is a spiteful lieutenant within the infamous [[Iron Circle]] mercenary troop. He is a [[tiefling]] clad in a black surplice embroidered with a gold-trimmed gray ring. Sturmik is armed with a dagger and a wand; he can cast the spell [[force blast]], as well as create [[illusory|illusion]] serpents that appear to crawl on and bite a target. 